Package: scRNAseqApp
Title: A single-cell RNAseq Shiny app-package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Jianhong",
             family = "Ou",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "jianhong.ou@duke.edu"))
Description: scRNAseqApp is a Shiny app package that allows users to visualize
    single cell data interactively. It was modified from ShinyCell and repackaged
    to a tool to show multiple data.
